\s MUCUNGUZI MUKUNDWA WABAMBWE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mucunguzi Mukundwa, Wabambwe ku giti Ufatwa nk’umwambuzi kubw’icaha canje. Intimba wishizeko n’amarushwa yose bimbwira yuko Unkunda, ni je Wahanirwa!\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Data arampeba mpagarik’ umushaha nyw’igikombe kirura kubw’ivyaha vyawe\bd*\bd . \bd*\bd Urukundo rwanje rugu-kiza kurimbuka\bd*\bd  ku\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd bwawe munyavyaha nar\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd i Golgotha.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Amaraso, n’ibikomere, n’igitsibo, gushishagurwa wumve ko hari kubwawe. Umubabaro wawe niwo nikoreye\bd*\bd ,\bd*\bd  raba kandi ureme k\bd*\bd u \bd*\bd Wagu\bd*\bd cu\bd*\bd nguye\bd*\bd .\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Kwubw’ urukundo rwawe, ndi hano Mukiza, mfata uko ndi kwose Warambabarijwe. N’umutima ukunze kuv’ubu mbeshweho Yesu kubw’ icubahiro cawe Mukiza.\bd*
